<figureCitation box="[643,725,1863,1889]" captionStart="FIGURE 27" captionStartId="13.[151,250,1834,1858]" captionTargetBox="[209,1380,202,1783]" captionTargetId="figure-17@13.[151,1436,181,1810]" captionTargetPageId="13" captionText="FIGURE 27. Neighbour-joining tree of 12 specimens of Acerocnema with COI sequences, including unique voucher number (numbers starting with CCDB are from this study), sequence length and GenBank accession number." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4690639" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4690639/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="524">Fig. 27</figureCitation>
) (see Discussion section for further details).
</paragraph>
